title: Matt Pryor from Radar State/The Get Up Kids
itunes:title: Matt Pryor from Radar State/The Get Up Kids
description:
Episode 334 - WELCOME TO 2019! Our first episode of the new year is actually, a return guest! Matt Pryor from The Get Up Kids plays in a new band called Radar State that is really, REALLY good and I had to have him back on. We discuss dad life, playing in a supergroup and touring Brazil. Trust me, don’t miss this episode.
